{\em KryptoKnight} is a general-purpose network security service originated 
at the IBM Research Lab in Z\"urich. The following KryptoKnight-related (well,
mostly related...) papers are available by anon FTP from jerico.usc.edu:

(Look for lines beginning with "%%%".)

@inproceedings{TvH93a,
 author = "G. Tsudik and E. {van Herreweghen}",
 title = "On Simple and Secure Key Distribution",
